=head1 DESCRIPTION

A structure that defines configuration settings for an application that
supports the JWT Bearer Token Authorization Grant. The
C<AuthorizedAudience> field is the aud claim. For more information, see
RFC 7523 (https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc7523).

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AuthorizedTokenIssuers => ArrayRef[L<Paws::SSOAdmin::AuthorizedTokenIssuer>]

A list of allowed token issuers trusted by the Identity Center
instances for this application.

C<AuthorizedTokenIssuers> is required when the grant type is
C<JwtBearerGrant>.



